&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nivi:&lt;/strong&gt; Unlike Schopenhauer, you are an industrial philosopher. Like an industrial designer, your philosophy is designed for the masses. People suggest you read the great books—Aristotle and Wittgenstein and all the supposedly great philosophers.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Free Markets Are Intrinsic to Humans</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/free-markets-are-intrinsic-to-humans/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2019 14:46:56 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/free-markets-are-intrinsic-to-humans/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/free-markets-are-intrinsic-to-humans.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
