&lt;h1 id="free-markets-are-intrinsic-to-humans"&gt;Free Markets Are Intrinsic to Humans&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mar 5 2019&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We use credits and debits to cooperate across genetic boundaries&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;
Overall capitalism [meaning free markets] is intrinsic to the human species. Capitalism is not something we invented. Capitalism is not even something we discovered. It is in us in every exchange that we have.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>